{"tid":2272934,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)睇住狗3 Watch Dogs: Legion","createTime":"2020-11-05T11:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T11:21:44.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3e136ffff743bdfbdf3eab0ce6c4049f040d5b","tid":2272934,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:20:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">玩唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4NTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=f6e3318e\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4NTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=60dc7c17\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4NTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=0de7678a\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/89/Watch_Dogs_Legion.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F89%2FWatch_Dogs_Legion.jpg&h=b8da41c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《看門狗：自由軍團》是一款以第三人稱視角遊玩的動作冒險遊戲。相較於前作，本作沒有固定的主角。玩家可以在招募大多數出現設定於前作《看門狗2》24年後、在2040年的開放世界的倫敦中的公民[3][4]，招募完成便可以操控該角色，一但角色觸發永久死亡的話就要選擇另一個角色來進行。如果一個角色被捕，玩家可以使用其他角色來拯救他們。一旦被招募，這些角色必須被指派到三個類別之一：戰鬥類、潛入類或駭客類。《看門狗：自由軍團》是一款自由度極高的遊戲，玩家可以操控開放世界的任何人，當玩家想要招募NPC（即非玩家角色）會有特定的任務，去讓你完成從而招募該NPC。當招募完成便可以操控該人。這款遊戲有酷炫的動作和物品，基本上各種NPC會有不同的技能、武器丶裝扮，不同的NPC就會有不同的任務，只要完成任務，便可以繼續使用該角色，或者選擇其他角色。在預告片中看到這款遊戲可以建立自己的反抗軍，的確這款遊戲可操控任何角色。 <br />\n<br />\n隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4NTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=13327c82\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4NTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=a50b063f\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39ba2384588af7a67dc90490d19b609de941777","tid":2272934,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}